              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "IVHoq",
                  "name": "Right Top Flourish",
                  "fill": "#c9a84c90",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "━━━━ ⚜ ━━━━",
                  "textAlign": "center",
                  "fontFamily": "Geist Mono",
                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "letterSpacing": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "RVCgj",
                  "name": "Right Body Para 1",
                  "fill": "#2a1a0a",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Three days hence I ventured into Farum Azula — that crumbling labyrinth suspended above the tempest. The Beastmen there do not know peace, only hunger. I found among their bones a tome, its pages sealed with dried ichor.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "Crimson Text",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "FQDTv",
                  "name": "Right Body Para 2",
                  "fill": "#2a1a0a",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "The tome speaks of a mending rune — a shard of the original Elden Ring, scattered beyond the Erdtree's sight. Whether this is hope or heresy I cannot yet discern. But I have copied its sigils here, between these parchment leaves, where the Two Fingers cannot reach.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "Crimson Text",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "K8X1X",
                  "name": "Right Body Para 3",
                  "fill": "#2a1a0a",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Tomorrow I ride for Leyndell. The capital still stands — barely — its streets choked with soldiers who have forgotten what they guard. I will walk those golden avenues one more time before the final battle.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "Crimson Text",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "CPwRo",
                  "name": "Right Divider",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 8,
                  "alignItems": "center",
                  "children": [
