                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "General of the Redmane army and heir to the legacy of Godfrey, First Elden Lord. Radahn studied gravitational magic under the centaurs of Sellia so that he might ride his beloved horse Leonard, even as the rot consumed him.\n\nHe starved rather than let his steed perish beneath his weight, until at last his mind was eaten away — and still he fought.",
